      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound BMW E46 M3, featuring the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing. This example features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, providing direct mechanical linkage and a visceral shifting experience. The chassis is well-sorted, including a reinforced rear subframe to mitigate common structural fatigue and a factory-spec M-Variable differential for optimal power distribution. While the exterior displays minor road-going patina, the core performance attributes\u2014including the high-pressure VANOS system and rod bearing service\u2014have been addressed. This is a driver-spec icon tuned for the purist who values linear power delivery and telepathic steering feedback.",
